snippet.title: 2D Roguelite Top-Down Roguelite Shooter - Hostile Lands Trailer - GameMaker
snippet.description:
Hostile Lands is a 2D top-down, Roguelike shooter where a crash landing is mistaken for an act of war. LOOT hundreds of unique guns. ENHANCE your skills. RESCUE surviving crew members and ESCAPE...if you can. 

Demo Available Now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3075890/Hostile_Lands/

Made with GameMaker

#indiegame #roguelike  #gamemaker
